name: MACRAMÉ KNOT
description: Macramé Knot is a midtone warm neutral color with a hint of gray, green and brown undertones and is part of our New Neutrals Collection. The added depth and complexity of the undertones blend to create a versatile neutral fit for any design style. Influences of natural woven materials and handcrafted artwork inspired Macramé Knot and is a lovely addition for an outdoorsy, cabin design aesthetic.

name: STUCCO RELIEF
description: Stucco Relief is a light, plaster warm neutral color with just a subtle touch of gray and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Versatile enough to be a backdrop color or stand on its own, Stucco Relief is inspired by the ancient art of molding stucco into decoration for walls, floors and ceilings. Revive this historic inspiration by pairing Stucco Relief with a balance of other subtle neutrals as a backdrop against gallery art.

name: ROCKY MOUNTAIN CLAY
description: Rocky Mountain Clay is a light, alluring warm neutral color and part of our New Neutrals Collection. With a subtle hint of gray and green undertones, this color is inspired by the many clay types potters use to create handcrafted ceramics. With its effortless hushed tones and calming effect, be inspired to paint Rocky Mountain Clay as a backdrop color to highlight a collection of art.

name: COUNTRY RUBBLE STONE
description: Country Rubble Stone is an elegant, light warm beige color with a subtle touch of gray. This cool brown color creates a soothing backdrop to any design style and is inspired by its namesake Country Rubble Stone. Understated and calming, this color is an ideal choice for both rustic and modern design styles.

name: THROWING CLAY
description: Throwing Clay is a subtle, light khaki warm neutral color with understated hints of green and brown undertones and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Resembling the color of potter's clay, this color is understated and relaxed, perfect for casual design styles. The comforting quality of this appealing neutral makes it an ideal choice for cozy minimalism.

name: TWISTED SISAL ROPE
description: Twisted Sisal Rope is a creamy, natural midtone shade of sand color and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Used for home projects such as gardening and crafts, Twisted Sisal Rope is an adaptable neutral, earthy color perfect for creating a relaxed mood in traditional and modern spaces. Use as a whole home color or as a backdrop neutral so other brighter hues.

name: TIMBER WOLF
description: Timber Wolf is an outdoorsy, midtone warm neutral color with a touch of green and gray undertones and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Reminiscent of the coat colors of the majestic timber wolf that has played a major character in many myths and fairytales, this saturated color creates a cozy, moody vibe and is ideal for boho and cottagecore aesthetics.

name: SQUIRREL'S TAIL
description: Squirrel's Tail is a midtone, stone beige color with touches of green and gray undertones and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Taking its name from the cute tail of the fuzzy outdoor visitors, Squirrel's Tail creates a sense of depth and is a lovely addition to design styles with lots of natural materials.

name: STEPPING STONE
description: Stepping Stone is an understated, light warm neutral color with the slight hint of green and is part of our New Neutrals Collection. Inspired by the phrase meaning to achieve something or something that helps someone advance, typically careerwise, Stepping Stone is perfectly balanced between warm and cool and is a versatile, sophisticated neutral color choice for both casually-rustic and modern-chic design styles.

name: AROMATIC CLOVES
description: Aromatic Cloves is a dark, mysterious and smoky warm neutral color with a hint of black and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Inspired by the strong, sweet aromatic spice, Aromatic Cloves is a grounding color rich in history and creates a dramatic backdrop to modern design styles.

name: INCENSE STICK
description: Incense Stick is an aromatic, pungent midtone brown color with a hint of green and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Inspired by the fragrant smoke once these sticks are lit, this color makes a lovely backdrop to meditation and yoga spaces.

name: ZESTY CORIANDER
description: Zesty Coriander is a midtone cool brown color with a touch of gray and green and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Inspired by the culinary spice used in a variety of dishes, this color is versatile enough for both rustic and refined spaces. Pair Zesty Coriander with subtle pink and pearl white colors, then add a finishing touch of gold and velvet for a chic design aesethic.

name: COFFEE GRINDS
description: Coffee Grinds is a deep, nutty brown color with a touch of gray and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Evoking the rich scents of mornings spent at the local coffee shops, Coffee Grinds is an organic, complex color that creates added depth to traditional and transitional spaces.

name: SMOKED OAK BROWN
description: Smoked Oak Brown is deep, smoky bronzed brown color with a hint of green and gray and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Intense and complex, Smoked Oak Brown is an enriching color with an organic quality, making it an ideal color for exterior spaces and interior cabinetry.

name: PRUNE THE TREE
description: Prune the Tree is a dark, smoky brown with a touch of olive green and gray undertones and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Playing on the phrase, "prune the tree," this complex, organic color captures the vitality of nature and creates visual impact on both interior and exterior spaces. The versatility of this enriching color also makes it an ideal choice for cabinetry and millwork.

name: CHIAROSCURO
description: Chiaroscuro is a dark, nocturnal brown color with the slightest touch of moss green and black and is part of our New Neutrals Collection. Inspired by the artistic skill of contrasting light and shadow, perfected by the Old Masters painters including Leonardo da Vinci, this dark neutral color creates drama and is an impactful choice for modern and traditional spaces.

name: TOBACCO INCENSE
description: Tobacco Incense is a spicy, smoky dark brown color with a touch of charcoal gray undertones and part of our New Neutrals Collection. Inspired by the instensely aromatic incense used as a home fragrance, Tobacco Incense is a deeply complex color that creates an impact. As an alternative to black and an alluring cross between charcoal and chocolate, showcase this color in interiors or exteriors for dramatic effect.

name: CHOCOLATE FIX
description: Chocolate Fix is a luxurious and decedant, deep shade of chocolate brown color with a touch of gray undertones and part of our New Neutrals Collection. This deliciously lush color envelopes a space for dramatic impact and is inspired by chocolate cravings. Pair with crisp white and shell pink for a feminine chic design aesthetic or add sumptuous depth to modern design styles.

name: ALMOND MILK
description: Almond Milk is an inviting, soft white color with a hint of warmth and part of our High Hide Whites Collection. With its creamy undertones and just a hint of yellow, Almond Milk adds depth and dimension to any space. As an excellent multipurpose white, Almond Milk works with a range of design styles including Traditional farmhouse and Modern loft aesthetics. This soft white color is a popular choice for walls, ceiling, trim and cabinetry and is a perfect all-over color for an open space plan.

name: WHITE DAISY
description: White Daisy is a refreshing white color with just a subtle hint of warmth and part of our High Hide Whites Collection. Delivering style and sophistication, White Daisy plays well with other colors, yet can stand on its own. Add White Daisy to a modern space for a clean look or to a traditional beachside cottage to balance out blue and green color schemes. Does your room face east or north? These rooms don’t get as much warm, natural light so to counterbalance these cooler, shady rooms, try White Daisy.

name: COCONUT GROVE
description: Coconut Grove is a clean white color with just a subtle hint of warmth and part of our High Hide Whites Collection. As a classic go-to white that appears clean and neutral in most lighting situations, Coconut Grove is an ideal color choice for dark wood accents and other natural materials. This elegant white color is also an excellent choice to pair with pastel color schemes.

name: SWISS MERINGUE
description: Swiss Meringue is a neutral, soft white color that balances warmth and coolness and is part of our High Hide Whites Collection. This alabaster shade of white is a versatile hue that can effortlessly pair with industrial design elements like metal or rustic elements like distressed woods. With its neutrality and very little undertones, Swiss Meringue is a perfect color choice for an all-white aesthetic or as a complement to jewel tones.

name: AT FIRST LIGHT
description: At First Light is a neutral white color with depth and part of our High Hide Whites Collection. As a neutral color, At First Light is a white color that can work with any design style and is perfect for both traditional and contemporary design projects. The softness of this neutral white color make it an ideal choice to design spaces that feels open and airy without feeling cold and complements spaces that get a lot of natural lighting.

name: NORTH TO ALASKA
description: North to Alaska is a cool, crisp and clean white color with a touch of gray and part of our High Hide Whites Collection. Reminding one of a snowy morning, this bright white color is versatile and will work for any design aesthetic. North to Alaska is a fresh, clean and modern white color, which makes it an excellent choice for trim and cabinetry, as well as modern and contemporary open spaces. This white color also pairs well with cool colors such as grays and blues.

name: SUGAR SWIZZLE
description: Sugar Swizzle color is a clean, cooler white with a subtle touch of gray undertones, offering both versatility and charm. This classic white has depth, making it a refreshing choice for modern spaces, particularly in open floor plans. Its light, airy quality is perfect for creating serene, minimalist atmospheres, while its muted sophistication makes it an excellent neutral backdrop. Whether used on its own or paired with other whites or cool grays, Sugar Swizzle lends elegance and dimension to any room without feeling too stark or cold.

name: CLASSIC WHITE
description: Classic White is a cooler, neutral white color and is part of our High Hide Whites Collection. Inspired by classic elegance and clean architecture, Classic White is a snowy white color and the ideal neutral shade for bright and airy spaces and is a perfect blank canvas for art-filled spaces. This cool white color is illuminating and pure, making it an ideal white color for whole home design or for use on trim, ceilings and cabinetry.

name: BE COOL
description: Be Cool is a cool, crisp white color and is part of our High Hide Whites Collection. Brilliant and sparkling with energy, Be Cool is an ideal white color for use on trim work and cabinetry. The more neutral, reflective quality of this cool white makes it a perfect choice for contemporary and modern architecture. This clean white pairs beautifully with grays and other cool color shades. Is your room south-facing? Cool white colors such as Be Cool are ideal choices to counterbalance the natural warming tones from southern exposure.

name: ICY WHITE
description: Icy White is a cool, snowy clean white color and is part of our High Hide Whites Collection. This cool, brilliant white conjures up images of winter wonderlands and provides a welcome ambiance to modern spaces. This versatile white color provides the perfect backdrop to artwork and brightens a room with limited natural lighting.

name: BEDROCK GRAY
description: Bedrock Gray is a muted, earthy gray with subtle undertones of taupe, evoking a sense of stability and timelessness.

name: SHADOW
description: Shadow is a dark, muted gray with cool undertones, offering a sleek and modern vibe.

name: WINDSWEPT WILLOW
description: Windswept Willow is a soft, earthy green with gray undertones, offering a calm, natural elegance.

name: TIDE AT DUSK
description: Tide at Dusk is a muted, dusky blue-gray offering a tranquil and balanced feel.

name: CANYON SUNSET
description: Canyon Sunset is a warm, earthy terracotta with rich undertones, capturing the essence of desert evenings.

name: FALLEN BARK
description: Fallen Bark is a warm, muted brown reflecting the hues of aged tree bark.

name: VINTAGE LEATHER
description: Vintage Leather is a warm, golden-brown, reminiscent of aged leather.

name: SUNDRIED TOMATO
description: Sundried Tomato is a rich, earthy red-brown with warm undertones, evoking the depth of sun-kissed tomatoes.

name: PLUM PUDDING MAHOGANY
description: Plum Pudding Mahogany is a moody, smoky majestic warm purple color with a hint of plum raisin and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. This sweet and spicy hue is inspired by the large trees dotted throughout South and Central America--also called Acajou, Tropical American Mahogany and Honduras Mahogany--and is used in classic furniture and cabinetmaking. Occasional logs produce several figures, curly, quilted, and the rare plum pudding figure which looks like large drips running down the board. Plum Pudding Mahogany is an ideal color for traditional home styles to add a touch of elegance.

name: GIANT SEQUOIA GROVE
description: Giant Sequoia Grove is a handsome, deep brown color with a touch of orange and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the visually-striking giant sequoia trees located only on the western slopes of the Sierra Nevada mountains in California, these immense, majestic trees bring a sense of peace and wonder. Giant Sequoia Grove is a perfect color choice for cabin retreats and desert modern abodes to bring relaxed elegance to a space.

name: REDWOOD FOREST CATHEDRAL
description: Redwood Forest Cathedral is a saturated, rich orange-tinged earthy red color and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by Cathedral Grove, a silent preserve and home to the tallest, oldest redwoods at Muir Woods, this color inspires quiet contemplation. Redwood Forest Cathedral looks inviting on both rustic and refined spaces.

name: I CUT THE CHERRY TREE
description: I Cut the Cherry Tree is a sweet, deep earthy red color with brown tones and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. A play on words to the classic myth of a young George Washington cutting down a cherry tree with his hatchet, this color embraces its tart cherry tones and is an ideal color choice for traditional architectural spaces.

name: FIRESIDE CHAT
description: Fireside Chat is a enriching, earthy, brick red color with warm orange tones and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by time spent outdoors by the fire with friends and family, this color inspires warm and cozy vibes. With its versatile undertones, Fireside Chat is an ideal color choice for both rustic and refined spaces. Pair Fireside Chat on a home with brick or a rustic barn for a touch of cottagecore, rural country aesthetic.

name: SEDONA SANDSTONE
description: Sedona Sandstone is a rustic, earthy midtone red color with brown tones and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the celebrated red sandstone rocks of Sedona, Arizona, this color is a vivid reminder of the natural color highlights throughout the American West. Sedona Sandstone is a perfect choice for Craftsman, desert modern and cabin retreats to highlight the connection to the outdoors.

name: REDWOOD
description: Redwood is a dense, earthy reddish brown color with orange undertones and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the Redwood National and State Parks, home to the tallest trees on Earth, this color highlights the national treasures dotting the rugged coastlines of California. Red-toned wood stains are classic color choices that have been a tradition for over 200 years because of its warm-hued tones and exotic look, and classic redwood color staining remains popular today. It’s an excellent wood stain for outdoor features, including decks, patios, barns and more.Bring a touch of majestic regalness to rustic spaces by choosing Redwood as an homage to outdoor living.

name: SECRET TREE HOUSE
description: Secret Tree House is a warm, earthy midtone brown color with orange undertones and is part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by treasured moments of childhood, Secret Tree House creates warm and cozy cocoon and is a modern version of the warm wood color found in many midcentury modern homes. This is an ideal color choice for anyone who loves the modern aesthetic paired with traditional design elements.

name: CHOCOLATE BROWN
description: Chocolate Brown is a deep, rich brown color with a hint of red undertones and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Decadent and enriching, this color is a natural alternative to black and creates a striking backdrop to other exterior design elements. Chocolate Brown is a forever classic and is ideal for traditional and modern spaces such as industrial, contemporary and minimalist aesthetics.

name: OAK BROWN
description: Oak Brown is a natural, earthy deep brown color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Understated and versatile enough for a variety of architectural styles, Oak Brown is an ideal color choice for both traditional and modern exteriors.

name: CHESTNUT BROWN
description: Chestnut Brown is a versatile, understated midtone brown color with a hint of yellow and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. The lighter tones of Chestnut Brown paired with the richness of brown create a univerally-appealing color that is an ideal choice for classic, traditional homes or modern homes with industrial touches. Try Chestnut Brown on your beach house for a touch of tropical vibes.

name: JACOBEAN RENAISSANCE
description: Jacobean Renaissance is a rich, dark brown color with a touch of yellow and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the second phase of Renaissance architecture in England that strongly influenced furniture styles of the time, including chairs and tables, this timeless dark stain color is a popular color choice and remains a classic choice for a variety of home exteriors including traditional and modern spaces.

name: GOLDEN OAK
description: Golden Oak is a timeless, warm honey color with a touch of brown and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the evergreen oak tree named as the national tree of Cyprus, the warm hues of this color stain pair perfectly with nature, lots of sunlight and colorful homes. Pair Golden Oak with a sage green hue on the home for a perfectly color-balanced touch of the outdoors.

name: RED CEDAR
description: Red Cedar is a warm, earthy brown color with a hint of red and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the dignified tree of its namesake observed at Roanoke Island, Virginia in 1564 and described by the early colonists as "the tallest and reddest cedars in the world," Red Cedar is a classic choice for traditional and modern architectural styles. Pair Red Cedar with weathered gray outdoor furnishings and a touch of blue and oatmeal accessories for classic, beachside style.

name: HANDCRAFTED
description: Handcrafted is a rustic, warm, midtone brown color with a touch of ochre orange and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the trend of creating objects by hand--whether artwork and furnishings, to home interiors and outdoor gardenscapes--Handcrafted highlights vintage and classic design. Stain your deck with Handcrafted, then place cushions, draperies, textiles and lighting to set a Boho-vintage oasis.

name: INTO THE WILD
description: Into the Wild is an earthy, warm midtone brown color with a touch of yellow and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the classic, award-winning children's book "Where the Wild Things Are," this color sparks a joy for outdoor living. Pair Into the Wild with charcoal gray and cool white for a classic exterior color palette.

name: SMOKED OAK
description: Smoked Oak is a rustic, warm neutral color with a touch of green and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the smoking process that naturally changes the color appearance on wood, this color is ideal for classically traditional and modern spaces. Pair Smoked Oak with gray blues and sage greens for a classic beachside retreat.

name: NEW CEDAR
description: New Cedar is a midtone warm neutral color with a touch of pink and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by fresh cut cedar wood planks, this versatile color helps create an oasis of calm to a backyard deck. Pair New Cedar with navy and crisp white for a classic Americana home aesthetic.

name: CABIN IN CANDLELIGHT
description: Cabin in Candlelight is a warm, honeyed tan color with a brown cast and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the romantic, cozy glow of a cabin's low lighting at dusk, this color creates at atmosphere worthy of any outdoor space. Pair Cabin in Candlelight with pine greens and charcoal grays for a space worthy of trendy #Cabincore vibes.

name: SWEET HONEY MAPLE
description: Sweet Honey Maple is a golden honey yellow color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the beautiful color of boiled maple to achieve a honey caste, this color is truly a sweet choice for any outdoor space. Pair Sweet Honey Maple with greens, creams and browns to achieve a #Cottagecore or Boho aesthetic.

name: OLIVE WOOD BRANCH
description: Olive Wood Branch is a soft, warm golden honey color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the richly colored wood prized for its appearance and texture, this color is an ideal choice for a Mediterranean-inspired space. Pair Olive Wood Branch with warm white, rust and brilliant blue to highlight this Mediterranean aesthetic and finish with a collection of olive trees.

name: RAW BALSA WOOD
description: Raw Balsa Wood is a natural, warm neutral color with a hint of green and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the rare tropical wood that hobbyists prize, this color is versatile and ideal for a wide variety of design styles. Pair Raw Balsa Wood with light grays and whites for a modern, Scandinavian aesthetic.

name: HIKING TRAILS
description: Hiking Trails is a rustic tan color with hints of green and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the breathtaking beauty of the surrounding view on a favorite hike, lighter stain colors like Hiking Trails are perfect for temperate climates, creating an unfussy, clean, yet elegant aesthetic. Pair this color with sage greens, ochre and warm white for a beachy aesthetic.

name: SCRUBLANDS HABITAT
description: Scrublands Habitat is a muted olive green color with a hint of yellow and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Incorporate a touch of Mother Nature to your home with Scrublands Habitat, a beautiful representation of the trendy organic design movement. Add natural wood furnishings, recycled textiles and DIY accessories for a touch of homey comfort.

name: PRAIRIE GRASSLAND
description: Prairie Grassland is a muted, sage green color with a hint of smoke and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Embrace the beauty of the color inspired by the prairie grassland ecosystems that are home to a wide variety of plant and wildlife. Pair Prairie Grassland with weathered gray furnishings, aged bronze accents and tweed textiles for classical charm.

name: RURAL WOODLANDS
description: Rural Woodlands is a soothing sage green color with hints of gray and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the beauty of the outdoors, Rural Woodlands is ideal for classic and modern design styles. Embrace nature by pairing this color with greiges, tans and rust for a connection to timeless style.

name: SMOKY BRUSHLAND
description: Smoky Brushland is a muted, sage green color with a hint of gray and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the brushland biomes containing a rich collection of flora and fauna, this color is ideal for modern or historic design styles. Pair Smoky Brushland with warm gray and golden yellows for a cozy, summer cabin vibe.

name: SAGE SMUDGE STICK
description: Sage Smudge Stick is a smoky, green-blue color with a hint of gray and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the Native American ritual of purifying a space, this color is versatile and ideal for a range of design styles. Pair Sage Smudge Stick with blue gray and cool white for a taste of beachside living.

name: WALK IN THE PARK
description: Walk in the Park is a lush, deep green color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Get outside and enjoy the sunshine! Walk in the Park provides ideal inspiration to go outside and spend time in nature. Pair this color with warm whites, earthy browns and sunshine yellows for a touch of #Cottagecore delight.

name: SECRET GARDEN
description: Secret Garden is a deep, blackened green color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the classic children's book, "The Secret Garden," create your own bit of the English countryside fantasy by pairing this color with rose bushes, iron work furnishings, and vintage textiles.

name: SEARED ASH
description: Seared Ash is a dark, moody blue gray color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the close-grained ash tree that has a proud history and connected to many legends. Norse mythology calls it "The World Tree." Create your own legendary backyard by pairing Seared Ash with true grays, warm greiges, sage greens, crisp whites and raw woods.

name: NAVAL SHIPYARD
description: Naval Shipyard is a deep navy blue color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Inspired by the historic shipyards at many ocean ports, this color is a tried-and-true classic, while trending again in modern outdoor designs. Pair Naval Shipyard with crisp whites and pastels for touch of unexpected youthful glamour.

name: STORMS AHEAD
description: Storms Ahead is a moody, midtone ocean blue color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. A timeless classic hue with a touch of drizzly raindrops creates a space that is at once cozy, yet cool. Create your own outdoor country garden escape from the storm by pairing Storms Ahead with garden floral textiles, pinks, corals, yellows, spring bulb greens and warm whites.

name: FADED BLUE CLAPBOARD
description: Faded Blue Clapboard is a midtone, weathered blue color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. A little bit country and a little bit coastal, this color is a peaceful, calm hue that is ideal for a variety of outdoor design styles. Pair Faded Blue Clapboard with crisp white furnishings and black and white striped textiles for classic, French-inspired charm.

name: FOSSILIZED WOOD
description: Fossilized Wood is a darker, moody blue gray color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. This strong, classic hue is sophisticated, yet reassuringly casual and ideal for both classic and modern styling. Pair Fossilized Wood with metal and raw woods for an industrial design aesthetic.

name: COLD AND RAINY
description: Cold and Rainy is a cool, drizzling blue gray color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Enjoy the peaceful serenity of this calming hue, ideal for a variety of design styles. Pair with cool whites, true grays and sage greens for a classic coastal aesthetic.

name: BRACING WINDS
description: Bracing Winds is a lighter, cool blue gray color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Calming and cool, this color creates a comfortable and timeless look to any design style. Pair with crisp whites and true grays for a minimalist, Scandinavian-inspired aesthetic.

name: MUSHROOM CAPS
description: Mushroom Caps is a cool, earthy greige color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Savor this neutral color that is ideal for a variety of design styles, including Craftsman bungalows and beachside cottage retreats.

name: PRESERVED PEWTER
description: Preserved Pewter is a sophisticated, warm gray color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. This elegant, casual neutral is ideal for most design styles, including Modern Farmhouse and Transitional.

name: WINTER'S EDGE
description: Winter's Edge is a light and airy, barely there gray color with a kiss of warmth and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. When just a hint of color will do, this always-in-style versatile color is ideal for any design style.

name: VINTAGE OAK
description: Vintage Oak is an earthy, midtone warm greige color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Embrace the vintage vibes of this hue by pairing Vintage Oak with weathered gray furnishings and aged bronze accessories. This classic pastoral hue is right at home with rustic ranch, as well as Cottagecore aesthetics.

name: SUNBLEACHED PINE
description: Sun-bleached Pine is a lighter khaki gray color with a hint of green and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. This stylish, timeless neutral color is ideal for historic and modern design styles and would fit right at home with Craftsman and modern industrial aesthetics.

name: EARLY AMERICAN CLASSIC
description: Early American Classic is an earthy, warm greige color with a hint of red and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Rooted in history, this timeless classic neutral color looks great on any space and is ideal for historic and Transitional design styles.

name: STEEP ESCARPMENT
description: Steep Escarpment is a midtone rustic, greige color with a hint of green and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. A stone neutral that is both stylish and classic, Steep Escarpment creates graceful spaces in any style and feels at home with rustic ranch, modern farmhouse and historic Craftsman spaces.

name: SILVER MINING
description: Silver Mining is a classic, light gray color with a hint of warm and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. A classic, staple hue feel sophisticated while at home with any design style, Silver Mining is an ideal choice for Transitional, as well as modern aesthetics.

name: COLLECTING DRIFTWOOD
description: Collecting Driftwood is a midtone, gray color with a hint of warmth and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Grounded in nature, this neutral gray color gives spaces a timeless, sophisticated quality. Collecting Driftwood is an ideal choice for beachside cottages and cabin retreats.

name: WINTER BRANCHES
description: Winter Branches is a darker, charcoal gray color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Strong and grounded, while hinting toward a modern edge, Winter Branches is a perfect choice for rustic and modern design styles. Add to Mid-century modern or industrial aesthetics for a final touch to the outdoor living spaces.

name: FRANCISCAN WALNUT
description: Franciscan Walnut is a dark, cool mocha brown color with a hint of gray and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. Subdued and smoky, Franciscan Walnut exudes style and sophistication. Make a statement by pairing this color with muted blues, metals and raw woods for a casual, classic aesthetic.

name: CORDOVAN BROWN
description: Cordovan Brown is a deep, rich, chocolatey brown color and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. A classic stain color known for generations, Cordovan takes its name from the city of Córdoba, Spain, where the production of cordovan leather was first practiced by the Visigoths in the seventh century. This color is an ideal choice for Mediterranean and Southwest design styles.

name: CARBONIZED WOOD
description: Carbonized Wood is a deep, bold charred black color with a hint of blue and part of our SOLID-COLOR Exterior Deck, Fence & Siding Stain Collection. This sleek color is sophisticated and sleek, making it an ideal choice for minimalist, modern and Scandinavian-inspired design styles.
